This is the counter to add counts.
for example: you can counter how many car in the parking lot by click "new counter" and clicker the counter just added, then it will take you to the counter adding page. Inside counting page you can click "add" to add counter,
click "reset" to reset
click "rename" to give it a new name
click "stats" to show counter history for counter, it will pop up a list view for that.

the delete a counter just long press counter in the mainpage, then it will be deleted.


